#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2458
msgid ""
"Review all Code element (PHP & HTML), SVG element (code), Query editor, and "
"\"echo\" tag instances."
msgstr ""
"Gennemgå alle Code-element (PHP & HTML), SVG-element (kode), Query-editor og "
"»echo« tag-forekomster."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2819
msgid ""
"Click the button above to retrieve all Code element, SVG element (code), "
"Query editor, and \"echo\" tag instances and review the code for every page, "
"template, etc."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen ovenfor for at hente alle Code-element, SVG-element (kode), "
"Query-editor og »echo« tag-forekomster og gennemgå koden for hver side, "
"skabelon osv."

