msgid "Function names must pass the check through the %s filter."
msgstr "Funktionsnavne skal bestå kontrollen gennem %s filteret."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2785
msgid ""
"Copy and paste the code below into your Bricks child theme to allow those "
"functions to be called through the \"echo\" tag. Remove the function names "
"you don't want to allow. Explore the %s documentation for more code examples "
"such as using regex for more flexible echo tag checks, etc."
msgstr ""
"Kopier og indsæt koden nedenfor i dit Bricks-underordnede tema for at "
"tillade, at disse funktioner kan kaldes gennem »echo«-tagget. Fjern de "
"funktionsnavne, du ikke ønsker at tillade. Udforsk %s dokumentationen for "
"flere kodeeksempler, såsom brug af regex for mere fleksible echo tag-"
"kontroller osv."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2826,
#: ../includes/elements/code.php:73, ../includes/elements/code.php:185,
#: ../includes/elements/svg.php:79
msgid "Code execution"
msgstr "Kodeudførelse"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2827
msgid "Allow specific user roles or individual users to execute code."
msgstr ""
"Tillad specifikke brugerroller eller individuelle brugere at udføre kode."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2844
msgid ""
"Code execution has been explicitly disabled by the %s filter. This filter is "
"currently overriding your Bricks settings."
msgstr ""
"Kodeudførelse er blevet eksplicit deaktiveret af %s filteret. Dette filter "
"tilsidesætter i øjeblikket dine Bricks-indstillinger."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2850
msgid "Enable code execution"
msgstr "Aktivér kodeudførelse"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2854
msgid ""
"Exercise great caution with granting code execution privileges. Enable them "
"sparingly and only for trusted roles or ideally only specific users. Grant "
"the least permissions necessary to maintain tight security."
msgstr ""
"Udvis stor forsigtighed med at tildele rettigheder til kodeudførelse. "
"Aktivér dem sparsomt og kun for betroede roller eller helst kun for "
"specifikke brugere. Tildel de mindst mulige tilladelser for at opretholde "
"stram sikkerhed."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2856
msgid ""
"Function names called through the \"echo\" tag must be whitelisted via the "
"%s filter."
msgstr ""
"Funktionsnavne, der kaldes gennem »echo«-tagget, skal være hvidlistet via %s-"
"filteret."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2858
msgid "User roles with code execution capability"
msgstr "Brugerroller med mulighed for kodeudførelse"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2887
msgid "Individual users with code execution capability"
msgstr "Individuelle brugere med mulighed for kodeudførelse"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2905
msgid ""
"Set code execution capability for individual users by editing their user "
"profile."
msgstr ""
"Indstil mulighed for kodeudførelse for individuelle brugere ved at redigere "
"deres brugerprofil."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2918
msgid ""
"Code that requires execution only runs when it has a valid code signature."
msgstr ""
"Kode, der kræver udførelse, kører kun, når den har en gyldig kodesignatur."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2919
msgid ""
"Regenerate code signatures whenever your WordPress salts (secret keys) "
"change."
msgstr ""
"Regenerér kodesignaturer, når dine WordPress-salte (hemmelige nøgler) ændres."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2923
msgid ""
"Please create a full-site backup and perform a \"Code review\" (see above) "
"before generating code signatures globally."
msgstr ""
"Opret venligst en fuld sikkerhedskopi af dit websted og udfør en "
"»Kodegennemgang« (se ovenfor), før du genererer kodesignaturer globalt."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2931
msgid ""
"Valid code signatures are required for all Code (element), SVG (element) and "
"Query editor instances to run."
msgstr ""
"Gyldige kodesignaturer er påkrævet for alle Kode (element), SVG (element) og "
"Query editor-instanser for at kunne køre."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2936
msgid "Regenerate code signatures"
msgstr "Regenerér kodesignaturer"

